resources.string: Join us for a lunch full of surprises! Are you really eating what you think you are? Come find out, and have a funky meal while you\'re at it!
Sick of eating Bistro Pizza or Ely Harvest smoothies everyday? Come try some authentic thai cuisine for lunch today! You might have a new favorite meal after today!
On the menu tonight: Easter Dinner! Come enjoy some ham, carrots and pototos for an Easter with your friends. Don\'t forget a chocolate bunny on the way out!
Help us celebrate Earth Day by enjoying some tasty sustainable, organic and locally grow foods! Consider participating in our recycled art contest, and win up to 20 owl bucks!
Hey commuter students! Stop by the Tekoa Room on your way to the Dining Commons for a free meal ticket. Lunch is on us today!
Let\'s start May with a bang! Today\'s May Day lunch will feature an enhanced salad bar, many tasty desserts, and live performances all day!
Take a break from studying and come indulge in some tasty treats. Back by popular demand, we have mozzarella sticks, fried mac and cheese, tenders, and so much more!
Did someone say Taco Tuesday? We did! Join us for the best Taco Tuesday you\'ve ever seen! If tacos aren\'t your thing, then try our burritos, quesadillas, and virgin margaritas!
"Kick off finals week with a huge brunch! Pancakes, waffles, french toast, eggs, bacon, sasague, hash browns, muffins, pastrys, orange juice.....endless possibilities. "
